SOMETIMES there’s too much of it, and at other times there isn’t enough. But money can ruin relationships! Studies indicate that couples often fight about spending habits and accuse each other of hiding money. They even make money decisions without talking to their partners. Daily Sun asked male SunReaders how they felt about dating a woman who has more money and a private bank account. Tendani Peri said: “As long as she gives me money for beers and petrol it’s fine.”